  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">INGO Aid to Care Danmark Adaptation Learning Programme for Africa</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CARE Denmark Adaptation Learning Programme for Africa operates in Niger, Ghana, Kenya and Mozambique. The objective is to strengthen the capacity of poor households to adapt to climate variability and change. The programme uses a community-based adaptation approach and it has special focus on women and vulnerable groups. Learning, application of collected information and spreading of the results are integral parts of the programme.</narrative>
  </description>
